data.title: Category:Irina Alexandrovna Romanova
data.text:
This category is for photographs of Princess Irina Alexandrovna of Russia (ru: Княжна Ирина Александровна Романова) (1895-1970), the daughter of Grand Duke Alexander Mikhailovich of Russia and Grand Duchess Xenia Alexandrovna of Russia; the wife of Prince Felix Yussupov, the killer of Rasputin.
